lead_paragraph: Byung Ho Park sat at his locker in the Minnesota Twins' spring training clubhouse, sipping a cup of iced coffee, oiling a first baseman's glove and interacting with teammates.

headline.print_headline: Korean Slugger Byung Ho Park Settles Into Life in the Majors
